# Paper Digest

A weekly, auto-curated roundup of new papers in **cardiovascular CFD, hemodynamics, and AI modelling** — PINN, neural operators, graph surrogates, diffusion/transformer/foundation models, digital twins. Papers are pulled from OpenAlex and arXiv, classified into one of six research tiers by Claude, and posted here every Monday morning (UTC).

**Who this is for:** cardiovascular CFD researchers, AI/ML modellers working on patient-specific simulation, digital-twin engineers, and clinicians who simulate. The goal is to keep *breadth awareness* cheap — ~15 curated papers/week, not an exhaustive literature review.

